main event: A civilian rancher spotted a silver, cigar-shaped object that was 60 ft long and 12 ft in depth, moving at a slow speed and suddenly disappearing in Fossil, Oregon on July 6, 1965.
interesting points: The object was described as a silver, cigar-shaped object.
The object was 60 ft long and 12 ft in depth.
The object was moving at a slow speed and suddenly disappeared.
The report was submitted to Project Blue Book, the U.S. Air Force's UFO investigation program.
The Air Force made efforts to contact the witness but was unsuccessful.
